FINRA Series 7 and Series 24 licenses;
Compliance experience at a broker-dealer preferred;
Team player and self-starter with the ability to manage time, juggle projects, work efficiently, and make reasoned judgments;
Excellent communication, writing and interpersonal skills;
Knowledge of Excel, DocuSign, SmartSheet, and Word, considered a plus. 

